Documentation
--------------
Available at the http://www.ge.infn.it/~geant4/hep/radmon/ website. For any
question please feel free to contact Riccardo Capra <capra@ge.infn.it>

Build instructions
-------------------
Run gmake

Syntax
-------
Run "Radmon -h" for syntax help. .startup.mac file is always run, if it
exists. An example of .startup.mac can be found in README directory

Radmon [-h|-H|-?] [-b] [-v] [<filename>]

-b option suppress interactive session
-v option sets the verbosity level
filename is run after .startup.mac, if present. Then interactive session
starts if -b is absent.

